  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2481310/extras/screen1.PNG?t=1689609619\" /></span><br><br>辩游记是第一款辩论主题角色扮演游戏。玩家可以按自己的节奏，推动主线剧情、探索支线故事、训练和备赛。同时，游戏将复刻现实中的辩论环节如：立论、答盘、质询、对辩、总结，再加上各种趣味技能和小游戏，让玩家体验游戏化后的辩论人生。<br><br>游戏的故事叙述是以主角王小明的视角，让玩家安排和操控王小明的辩论日常<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2481310/extras/screen2.PNG?t=1689609619\" /></span><br><br>玩家需要自主安排王小明的训练、备赛、听课、模辩等辩论日常。甚至可以触发和不同角色的支线剧情。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2481310/extras/prepare.PNG?t=1689609619\" /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2481310/extras/lesson.PNG?t=1689609619\" /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2481310/extras/sidemission.PNG?t=1689609619\" /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2481310/extras/mobian.PNG?t=1689609619\" /></span><br><br>做为辩论游戏，当然少不了和不同辩手一较高下的辩论赛事。玩家将操控小明挑战不同级别的辩论赛事。过程中还可以学到各种不同的趣味技能。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2481310/extras/screen4.PNG?t=1689609619\" /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2481310/extras/screen5.PNG?t=1689609619\" /></span><br><br>辩游记包含序章共有10个章节，每个章节都探讨不同辩题，再加上交由玩家自主安排日常的游戏模式，每个玩家都可以体验一套属于自己的辩论游戏记录。",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2481310/extras/screen1.PNG?t=1689609619\" /></span><br><br>辩游记是第一款辩论主题角色扮演游戏。玩家可以按自己的节奏，推动主线剧情、探索支线故事、训练和备赛。同时，游戏将复刻现实中的辩论环节如：立论、答盘、质询、对辩、总结，再加上各种趣味技能和小游戏，让玩家体验游戏化后的辩论人生。<br><br>游戏的故事叙述是以主角王小明的视角，让玩家安排和操控王小明的辩论日常<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2481310/extras/screen2.PNG?t=1689609619\" /></span><br><br>玩家需要自主安排王小明的训练、备赛、听课、模辩等辩论日常。甚至可以触发和不同角色的支线剧情。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2481310/extras/prepare.PNG?t=1689609619\" /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2481310/extras/lesson.PNG?t=1689609619\" /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2481310/extras/sidemission.PNG?t=1689609619\" /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2481310/extras/mobian.PNG?t=1689609619\" /></span><br><br>做为辩论游戏，当然少不了和不同辩手一较高下的辩论赛事。玩家将操控小明挑战不同级别的辩论赛事。过程中还可以学到各种不同的趣味技能。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2481310/extras/screen4.PNG?t=1689609619\" /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2481310/extras/screen5.PNG?t=1689609619\" /></span><br><br>辩游记包含序章共有10个章节，每个章节都探讨不同辩题，再加上交由玩家自主安排日常的游戏模式，每个玩家都可以体验一套属于自己的辩论游戏记录。",
